The paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, specifically the concepts of independent sets and matchings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). The paper also involves the study of graphs and their properties, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The concept of critical independent sets involves optimization, which could be categorized under cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) or cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
